metadata.name: Asaasins Genesis 1
metadata.description:
Asaasins Genesis is the first mint of Asaasins: The premier NFT club for entrepreneurs and operators in the software or general startup space. 

More information at https://www.asaasins.vip/

Asaasins Genesis holders get the following benefits:
✅ Access to mastermind of startup entrepreneurs
✅ $450K+ in exclusive discounts and benefits (inc Brex, deel, Pilot, Hubspot, CoinLedger & more)
✅ Private (professional) Discord
✅ Access to future mints & free airdrops 
✅ Private events & more
✅ All guided by proven founders and 1st-class advisory board
✅ & much more to come!
